===Etymology===
Partly from {{etyl|xme|grc}} {{m|xme|sc=Latn|*Arēvand}}, from {{etyl|ira|grc}} {{m|und|sc=Latn|*Raivant-}}, {{m|und|sc=Latn|*Rayivant-||possessing wealth}}; see Old Armenian {{term|Երուանդ|lang=xcl}} for more. And partly from {{etyl|xme|grc}} {{m|xme|sc=Latn|*Arvand}}; compare Avestan {{term||𐬀𐬎𐬭𐬎𐬎𐬀𐬧𐬝-|swift|lang=ae}}. The name of the river is from the second only.

